# Local-only Claude Code / vendor artifacts (not committed from the source repo)
# — except the dev-skills symlinks committed at the repo root, which give every
# developer auto-discovery of the maintenance skills under dev-skills/ without
# a per-machine setup step. See AGENTS.md > dev-skills/.
.claude/*
!.claude/skills
.codex/
.cursor/*
!.cursor/skills
.agents/*
